Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.28,0:00:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为所有人都怕你们就错了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.28,0:00:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是杰哈特·葛雷德同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.85,0:00:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好好相处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.14,0:00:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.89,0:00:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它会保护你和你最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起来！ 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是杰哈特 发现目标
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.09,0:00:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小看我！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.12,0:00:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达从视野里消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.09,0:00:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「维甘」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.59,0:00:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是移民计划失败的受害者们…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.74,0:00:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被遗弃在火星圈的人们…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.82,0:01:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建立起的新兴国家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.02,0:01:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被迫在严酷环境下生活的他们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.19,0:01:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为夺回那座名为「地球」的乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.98,0:01:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,策划起了规模宏大的计划
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.71,0:02:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维甘袭击事件的后续报道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.56,0:02:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军方发言人宣称
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:03:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次袭击事件中无人伤亡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.42,0:03:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 关于维甘机动战士的入侵途径
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据称还在调查中…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到处都在说这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 维甘攻来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过就算他们再来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台白色机动战士也会把他们打回老家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.15,0:03:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.71,0:03:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜啊 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.02,0:03:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没赶上昨天那场战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,场面可大了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 从没见过那种白色机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.64,0:03:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是军队的新机型吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.03,0:03:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.14,0:03:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆 千万记住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你驾驶高达的事要绝对保密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.25,0:03:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维甘的目标恐怕是高达
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.97,0:03:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白其中的含义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.79,0:04:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆知道什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.94,0:04:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老爸是军人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有小道消息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 老爸只字未提
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.62,0:04:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 罗玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是想加入我们社团了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.19,0:04:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来为昨天的事道谢的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.39,0:04:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 关于那件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道 要保密是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们俩的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.99,0:04:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.83,0:04:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待比赛那天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.91,0:04:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.38,0:04:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙 什么时候勾搭上的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗 青春就是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友情和恋情和机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.11,0:04:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:05:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有友情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.16,0:05:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只差恋情了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正明白就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我也有同感
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的青春从此开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然联邦军进行了情报管制
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是通过战斗发生的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和现场残留的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经圈定了高达的所在区域
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必你也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.05,0:05:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是以锻造机动战士闻名的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.44,0:05:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日野家族的私人宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆的父亲是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球联邦军总部BIGRING司令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原高达驾驶者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样说来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达被藏匿在亚瑟姆家的可能性极高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只换轴承果然作用不大…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说 我也想加入机动战士社团
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.32,0:06:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次自己说没兴趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏威 有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.34,0:06:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定可以帮上你们的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.02,0:06:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起 太厉害了 杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.73,0:06:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,程序稍作调整就变化这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 允许你加入
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离大会不远了 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.76,0:07:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别硬掰 夏威
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄坏的话就前功尽弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别…担心 就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:08:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗玛丽！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.66,0:09:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点 夏威
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.06,0:09:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 罗玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.30,0:09:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就说加点机油吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.32,0:09:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要的零件全在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.26,0:10:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎略显疲态
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.69,0:10:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调查的进展如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.93,0:10:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 除一个地方以外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经搜遍了整个地区
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.60,0:10:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果和之前相同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.40,0:10:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日野家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达就藏在明日野家里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点确信无疑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.61,0:10:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那里警卫森严…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.63,0:10:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.28,0:10:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你确定？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.38,0:10:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来这里不是为做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须赶紧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.69,0:10:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为实现维甘的夙愿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.19,0:10:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去我家？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你父亲是BIGRING的司令吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.83,0:10:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里有很多机动战士的相关资料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.73,0:11:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有是有 但那是爸爸的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能随便给别人看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定能找到提高性能用的珍贵资料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了变得更强 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.06,0:11:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想在比赛里获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让老爸见识下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事后再向父亲道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是为了让我们的机体变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.45,0:11:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.14,0:11:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过别乱翻哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.59,0:11:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去下父亲的书房
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以乱碰里面的东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.26,0:12:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群有意思的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个长发的人好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.00,0:12:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.78,0:12:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是BIGRING司令的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士相关的书是这本…这本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 我去厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿着走廊 到底右拐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.84,0:12:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这幢房子不像能藏得下机动战士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.71,0:12:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 剩下的可能性…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到了 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一天终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.49,0:13:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士模拟格斗大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.80,0:13:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托尔迪亚的年轻技师们齐聚一堂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.97,0:13:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装配机动战士和负责操纵的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部是学生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的智慧 热情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将在此碰撞出炽热的火花！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.24,0:13:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的愿望只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗 获胜 夺冠！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.98,0:13:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是48支队伍中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.48,0:13:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够如愿以偿的只有一队
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.95,0:13:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是那支队伍最后胜出
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获得荣耀的桂冠呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.74,0:13:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.78,0:14:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一场就是决赛了 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.81,0:14:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.86,0:14:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才就一直没看见他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 计划按时开始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会马上前往汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一支进入决赛的队伍出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.66,0:14:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈特曼校队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶者是法比·德鲁斯缇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别拍对手队伍了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给亚瑟姆镜头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:14:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡格斯大人 那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.94,0:15:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.95,0:15:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离决赛开始不到5分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.03,0:15:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特干什么去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.77,0:15:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.75,0:15:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维甘的机动战士又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你去哪 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决赛马上开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 这里拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.51,0:15:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回来 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.47,0:16:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们虽然在迎战 但坚持不了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.48,0:16:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们拦不住敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小的麻烦 但无碍大局
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 趁我不在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.18,0:17:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.36,0:17:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开火 开火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 又来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.24,0:17:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.59,0:17:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙无耻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.20,0:17:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.15,0:18:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜负已分了 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.55,0:18:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.33,0:18:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.11,0:18:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速战速决
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.59,0:18:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙哪来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.38,0:18:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援兵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.25,0:18:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡格斯大人 情况不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 再等会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 设定完成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尝尝这招
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪里去了 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.26,0:19:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.24,0:20:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.81,0:20:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是得给我老实点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.35,0:20:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险 罗玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.24,0:20:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快离开这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦军的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.40,0:20:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 拖延太久
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.45,0:21:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.54,0:21:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.68,0:21:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果大会改期了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.30,0:21:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 据说维甘又来进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.62,0:21:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 还是被那台白色机动战士打回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.74,0:21:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.09,0:21:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.28,0:21:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 亚瑟姆和杰哈特呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天他们请假
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.24,0:21:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.85,0:21:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是菲利特麾下的联邦军设施
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.61,0:21:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把高达藏在这里可以放心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 菲利特会保护我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论遇到什么敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.03,0:21:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达被运出明日野家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.72,0:22:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前去向不明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.14,0:22:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.31,0:22:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达乌内斯总部下令
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.66,0:22:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续潜伏直至成功夺取高达
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.37,0:22:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.28,0:22:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.08,0:22:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我刚才松了一口气？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.98,0:22:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.91,0:24:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业仪式 与好友的告别
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.73,0:24:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为战士的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.52,0:24:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是悲剧的开始吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.61,0:24:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 机动战士高达AGE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.90,0:24:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业仪式上的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.87,0:24:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个人的命运成就历史
